Add $40+30$ then add $8$ then add $5$:

$\begin{align}
\blueE{48}+\purpleD{35}&=\blueE{40}+\blueE{8}+\purpleD{30}+\purpleD5\\\\
&= \blueE{40}+\purpleD{30}+\blueE{8}+\purpleD{5}
\end{align}$

**Yes**, this strategy works.

